text: There was an issue with Adobe Acrobat putting the Registration window in your face and not letting you open a PDF.  I am currently uninstalling and reinstalling it with the proper settings to make it work right.  FYI

If anyone is a user of the Vim text editor from unix-land, gVim is available on the desktop.  If you haven't used it, it's a high-powered text editor with a steep learning curve, but sometimes is a necessary tool for data wrangling (I'd probably be helping you if that's the case, which is why I'm putting it on every server)
